the issue: https://github.com/geneontology/go-ontology/issues/31945\\n\\nThanks, \",\n      \"createdAt\": \"2026-04-29T18:05:29Z\",\n      \"includesCreatedEdit\": false,\n      \"isMinimized\": false,\n      \"minimizedReason\": \"\",\n      \"reactionGroups\": [],\n      \"url\": \"https://github.com/geneontology/go-ontology/issues/31945#issuecomment-4346271387\",\n      \"viewerDidAuthor\": false\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"IC_kwDOAkAHws8AAAABAw855w\",\n      \"author\": {\n        \"login\": \"raymond91125\"\n      },\n      \"authorAssociation\": \"MEMBER\",\n      \"body\": \"@dragon-ai-agent please obsolete GO:0003400 regulation of COPII vesicle coating and then rename GO:0048208 and GO:0006901 according to the comment from ValWood.\",\n      \"createdAt\": \"2026-04-29T18:09:10Z\",\n      \"includesCreatedEdit\": false,\n      \"isMinimized\": false,\n      \"minimizedReason\": \"\",\n      \"reactionGroups\": [\n        {\n          \"content\": \"EYES\",\n          \"users\": {\n            \"totalCount\": 1\n          }\n        }\n      ],\n      \"url\": \"https://github.com/geneontology/go-ontology/issues/31945#issuecomment-4346296807\",\n      \"viewerDidAuthor\": false\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"IC_kwDOAkAHws8AAAABAw9HFA\",\n      \"author\": {\n        \"login\": \"dragon-ai-agent\"\n      },\n      \"authorAssociation\": \"MEMBER\",\n      \"body\": \"🤖 Working on it...\\n\\nFollow along: [View workflow run](https://github.com/geneontology/go-ontology/actions/runs/25125757529)\\n\\n*— @dragon-ai-agent*\",\n      \"createdAt\": \"2026-04-29T18:09:38Z\",\n      \"includesCreatedEdit\": false,\n      \"isMinimized\": false,\n      \"minimizedReason\": \"\",\n      \"reactionGroups\": [],\n      \"url\": \"https://github.com/geneontology/go-ontology/issues/31945#issuecomment-4346300180\",\n      \"viewerDidAuthor\": true\n    }\n  ],\n  \"title\": \"Obsoletion request: GO:0003400\\t regulation of COPII vesicle coating\",\n  \"url\": \"https:/